fields.description:
I want to build some older code on an updated titanium but the build refuses with an error. the log tells me "!MESSAGE Unable to create menu item "com.appcelerator.titanium.mobile.command.install.blackberry", command "com.appcelerator.titanium.mobile.command.install.blackberry" not defined"

I understand that, I didn't include any blackberry code in it, at least not consciously. Do you now where I can find this?
fields.summary: can't build to device, error on build

comments.body:
What SDK are you using? What version of Titanium Studio? We need more details in order to help you. Can you pull the log from Studio and paste it here?

Titanium Studio -> Help -> Studio -> View Log File

Thanks.
